# 📅 Day 10 – LEFT JOIN & RIGHT JOIN

## Topics Covered

- LEFT JOIN
- RIGHT JOIN

## Brief Explanation

LEFT JOIN returns all rows from the left table and matching rows from the right table.

### Example

```sql
SELECT *
FROM A
LEFT JOIN B
ON A.id = B.id;
```

